OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782755283
OL,3,CMan who created fake Tinder profile to
OL,4,Centice strangers to 'rape' ex jailed
OL,6,F"Obsessive" Hussain set up the account
OL,7,Fa month after she ended their
OL,8,Frelationship when he assaulted her,
OL,9,Fdevising the plan to lure strangers to
OL,10,Fher home.
OL,12,FCheshire Police described it as "one
OL,13,Fof the most disturbing" cases it had
OL,14,Fever investigated.
OL,16,F"Assad Hussain was highly obsessive,"
OL,17,FPC Keith Terrill from Cheshire Police
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782755283
OL,3,CMan who created fake Tinder profile to
OL,4,Centice strangers to 'rape' ex jailed
OL,6,F"The amount of effort that he put into
OL,7,Fcarrying out the offences is extremely
OL,8,Falarming and quite unique but also I
OL,9,Fthink it's extremely deceitful.
OL,11,F"He went to a lot of effort to prevent
OL,12,Fthe victim finding out who he actually
OL,13,Fwas and he went to a lot of effort to
OL,14,Fobstruct the investigation."
OL,16,FIn a victim impact statement, read to
OL,17,Fcourt, the woman said "no should mean
OL,18,Fno".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782755283
OL,3,CMan who created fake Tinder profile to
OL,4,Centice strangers to 'rape' ex jailed
OL,6,F"I am grateful for the sentence that
OL,7,Fthe Judge has imposed on Mr Hussain
OL,8,Ftoday, this will bring me some peace
OL,9,Fover the coming months," she said.
OL,11,F"However, no sentence takes away the
OL,12,Fenormous impact his behaviour has had
OL,13,Fon both myself and my daughters.
OL,15,F"No person has the right to make me
OL,16,Ffeel unsafe in my own home just
OL,17,Fbecause I no longer want to date them.
OL,18,FNo should mean no.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782755283
OL,3,CMan who created fake Tinder profile to
OL,4,Centice strangers to 'rape' ex jailed
OL,6,F"Now I am left wondering how many men
OL,7,Fhave my address and believe I want to
OL,8,Fbe sexually assaulted, or worse.
OL,10,F"I appreciate today has delivered some
OL,11,Fclosure and the criminal justice
OL,12,Fprocess is at an end however, Mr
OL,13,FHussain has never shown any remorse,
OL,14,Fnever accepted responsibility and I
OL,15,Fknow I will never understand why or
OL,16,Freceive an apology. That alone has
OL,17,Fbeen difficult to accept."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782755283
OL,3,CMan who created fake Tinder profile to
OL,4,Centice strangers to 'rape' ex jailed
OL,6,FChester Crown Court heard Hussain
OL,7,Ffirst contacted the woman using the
OL,8,Ffake name 'Mick Renney' in April 2024,
OL,9,Fand they went on several dates.
OL,11,FAs the relationship developed, Hussain
OL,12,Fbecame "increasingly controlling" and
OL,13,Fon one occasion going to her house
OL,14,Fbecause she had a male friend
OL,15,Fvisiting, repeatedly ringing the
OL,16,Fdoorbell for two hours.
OL,18,FHe only left after a neighbour called
OL,19,Fthe police.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782755283
OL,3,CMan who created fake Tinder profile to
OL,4,Centice strangers to 'rape' ex jailed
OL,6,FThe relationship came to an end when,
OL,7,Fon 6 May 2024, the woman awoke to find
OL,8,FHussain had taken her mobile phone and
OL,9,Fread through her messages to male
OL,10,Fcolleagues and friends.
OL,12,FHe then bombarded the victim with
OL,13,Fquestions, demanding to know if she
OL,14,Fwas seeing other men, and when she
OL,15,Ftried to go to the bathroom with her
OL,16,Fphone, Hussain objected, forcing his
OL,17,Fway in and pushing her over.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782755283
OL,3,CMan who created fake Tinder profile to
OL,4,Centice strangers to 'rape' ex jailed
OL,6,FHe made several attempts to rekindle
OL,7,Fthe relationship, and contacted her
OL,8,Fdaughter and friends, accusing her of
OL,9,Fcheating on him.
OL,11,FIn July 2024, men began attending her
OL,12,Fhome address saying they had matched
OL,13,Fwith her on the dating app Tinder and
OL,14,Fshe had invited them round.
OL,16,FOn one night in August 2024, four men
OL,17,Fattended her address one after
OL,18,Fanother, all reportedly having
OL,19,Freceived almost identical messages.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782755283
OL,3,CMan who created fake Tinder profile to
OL,4,Centice strangers to 'rape' ex jailed
OL,6,FOther men turned up at her home and
OL,7,Ftold her that her messages said she
OL,8,Fwanted to engage in a "rape fantasy"
OL,9,Fand that she wanted to be "roughed up."
OL,11,FThey had also explained they had been
OL,12,Fled to believe that if she said "no"
OL,13,Fit meant she "wanted it more".
OL,15,FAnother man broke a glass panel at her
OL,16,Fhome after forcing the front door
OL,17,Fopen, showing her messages from the
OL,18,Ffake Tinder account telling him he
OL,19,Fshould give the door a "shove" as it
OL,20,Fwas "stiff".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782755283
OL,3,CMan who created fake Tinder profile to
OL,4,Centice strangers to 'rape' ex jailed
OL,6,FLater that day, one man entered her
OL,7,Fhome for several minutes before
OL,8,Fleaving, whilst her teenage daughter
OL,9,Fwas alone upstairs.
OL,11,FTo pretend to be the victim, Hussain
OL,12,Fhad to travel from South Manchester
OL,13,Finto central Cheshire to operate the
OL,14,Faccounts.
OL,16,FEnquiries showed he would often travel
OL,17,Fin the late evenings and stay in a lay-
OL,18,Fby just miles from her home address,
OL,19,Fwhere he would sit for hours at a time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782755283
OL,3,CMan who created fake Tinder profile to
OL,4,Centice strangers to 'rape' ex jailed
OL,6,FHussain was only caught after several
OL,7,Fof the men involved gave their details
OL,8,Fto detectives to help track down the
OL,9,Fsource of the fake accounts.
OL,11,FWhen the police could not find the
OL,12,Fvictim's ex-boyfriend Mick Renney on
OL,13,Fany of their systems, the force
OL,14,Fexamined doorbell footage and traced
OL,15,Fhis car back to Hussain's business.
OL,17,FOfficers discovered he had changed his
OL,18,Fcar registration, and used multiple
OL,19,Fmobile phones to maintain his alter-
OL,20,Fego and run the Fake Tinder accounts.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782755283
OL,3,CMan who created fake Tinder profile to
OL,4,Centice strangers to 'rape' ex jailed
OL,6,FHussain was found guilty of stalking
OL,7,Fafter a nine-day trial at Chester
OL,8,FCrown Court and has been sentenced.
OL,10,FFollowing the conviction,
OL,11,Finvestigating officer PC Keith Terrill
OL,12,Fsaid: "This is one of the most
OL,13,Fdisturbing stalking cases Cheshire
OL,14,FConstabulary has ever investigated.
OL,16,F"Hussain is an extremely deceitful
OL,17,Findividual whose only objective was to
OL,18,Fcause maximum harm to the victim and
OL,19,Fher children, even going as far as to
OL,20,Fincite others to break into her home
OL,21,Fand sexually assault her.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782755283
OL,3,CMan who created fake Tinder profile to
OL,4,Centice strangers to 'rape' ex jailed
OL,6,F"At no point has Hussain taken any
OL,7,Fresponsibility for his actions or
OL,8,Frecognised the sheer horror he came
OL,9,Fclose to unleashing."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
